1
00:01:47,308 --> 00:01:50,211
A little voice inside
 told me you were hungry.

2
00:01:50,244 --> 00:01:54,715
My soul is starved
 for perfection,
 margot, not food.

3
00:01:54,748 --> 00:01:57,218
Starved for a kind word 
 or two...

4
00:01:57,251 --> 00:01:59,420
From a world
 that hates me,

5
00:01:59,453 --> 00:02:03,291
a world that would love
to see my work burned
if it could.

6
00:02:03,324 --> 00:02:06,160
It's not your time,
 vincent.

7
00:02:06,194 --> 00:02:08,296
The world hasn't
 woken up to you.

8
00:02:08,329 --> 00:02:11,832
My time...
 Will never come.

9
00:02:11,865 --> 00:02:15,469
Perhaps it will.

10
00:02:15,503 --> 00:02:18,306
Listen to this,
 and look at that.

11
00:02:18,339 --> 00:02:20,508
Critics-- the way
they attack me
and lash out at me,

12
00:02:20,541 --> 00:02:23,344
like a coiled snake
with poison venom!

13
00:02:23,377 --> 00:02:25,446
I'll listen later.

14
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:30,184
I've prepared something
 special to warm the cockles
 of your heart.

15
00:02:30,218 --> 00:02:32,186
What is it?

16
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:35,256
Eat. I'll answer
 your questions later.

17
00:02:35,289 --> 00:02:39,527
Better I should starve
 and end my torment.

18
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:43,564
But it does smell good.
Just a little.

19
00:02:47,335 --> 00:02:50,638
It is good!
 What is it?

20
00:02:50,671 --> 00:02:53,907
It's a special brew
 for you, my friend.

21
00:02:55,476 --> 00:02:57,745
Potato potion.
 A potion?

22
00:02:57,778 --> 00:03:02,316
A brew? Some
sort of witchcraft?

23
00:03:02,350 --> 00:03:08,289
A family secret.
 Gaze into the bowl.
 What do you see?

24
00:03:09,257 --> 00:03:13,827
I see... Flowers.

25
00:03:13,861 --> 00:03:17,531
Many kinds of flowers.

26
00:03:17,565 --> 00:03:22,002
[ Margot ] you will become 
 the greatest painter of 
 flowers who ever lived,

27
00:03:22,035 --> 00:03:25,973
and one day, the flowers 
 will return your love.

28
00:03:27,375 --> 00:03:30,210
How will the flowers
 do that?

29
00:03:32,346 --> 00:03:36,284
After your body
 lies dead and still
 in the cold ground...

30
00:03:36,317 --> 00:03:38,752
For more than a century,

31
00:03:38,786 --> 00:03:42,523
the flowers will summon you
 back among the living.

32
00:03:42,556 --> 00:03:46,960
- but only for 100 days.
 - why only 100 days?

33
00:03:46,994 --> 00:03:50,598
That will be time enough
 for you to set right...

34
00:03:50,631 --> 00:03:53,534
All the things that have
 gone wrong in your life...

35
00:03:53,567 --> 00:03:55,836
This time.

36
00:03:55,869 --> 00:04:01,942
And then, vincent, you will 
 be able to rest in peace.

